{
  "text": "Due to the development of antibiotic resistance and the outbreak of infectious diseases caused by resistant pathogenic bacteria, pharmaceutical companies and researchers are now searching for new unconventional antibacterial agents. The demand for individualized therapy and lower risks of adverse effects has always been a goal for health professionals. Besides, new pharmaceutical formulations seeking to increase efficiency and reduce drug toxicity are currently being researched [CITATION_1] .",
